        "body": "### Checklist\r\n\r\n- [X] I am able to reproduce the bug with the [latest version](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/releases/latest).\r\n- [X] I made sure that there are *no existing issues* - [open](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/issues) or [closed](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed) - which I could contribute my information to.\r\n- [X] I have read the [FAQ](https://newpipe.net/FAQ/) and my problem isn't listed.\r\n- [X] I have taken the time to fill in all the required details. I understand that the bug report will be dismissed otherwise.\r\n- [X] This issue contains only one bug.\r\n- [X] I have read and understood the [contribution guidelines](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/blob/dev/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md).\r\n\r\n### Affected version\r\n\r\n0.25.1\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the bug\r\n\r\nThis issue particularly shows up on the \"Monstercat Uncaged\" playlist, with 401 songs as of April 8th.\r\n1. Open NewPipe;\r\n2. If not already, select the SoundCloud source;\r\n3. Search \"Monster Uncaged\" _or_ access it if it's saved;\r\n4. Tap the playlist (it has 401+ songs)\r\n5. Some elements will briefly load, but...\r\n6. You end up with a \"No videos\" error.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThe playlist should correctly load, listing the first songs (sorted by upload date or not), and load the next songs by scrolling.\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nThe playlist fails to load with error message \"No videos\", and a disappointed Lenny.\r\n\r\n### Screenshots/Screen recordings\r\n\r\n![Screenshot_20230408_184931_NewPipe](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24714832/230733710-33730226-8963-4187-a236-97485fed4e38.png)\r\n**Fig. 1: the saved playlist**\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Screenshot_20230408_184906_NewPipe\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24714832/230733734-9ff7449d-3bfc-4327-a491-1cb452cd3bb2.png\" width=285 />\r\n**Fig. 2: the playlist failing to load**\r\n\r\n### Logs\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n### Affected Android/Custom ROM version\r\n\r\nOneUI 5.1 (Android 13)\r\n\r\n### Affected device model\r\n\r\nSamsung Galaxy A71 4G (SM-A715F/DS)\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\n\r\n- playlist exists and is public on SoundCloud\r\n- attempted on fresh install of NewPipe\r\n- attempted on Wi-Fi with 433 Mbit/s (≈ 54 Mb/s)\r\n- disabled VoLTE due to Exynos vulnerability\r\n- disabled \"Calls over Wi-Fi\" due to Exynos vulnerability",
