        "body": "### Checklist\n\n- [X] I made sure that there are *no existing issues* - [open](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/issues) or [closed](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed) - which I could contribute my information to.\n- [X] I have read the [FAQ](https://newpipe.net/FAQ/) and my problem isn't listed.\n- [X] I'm aware that this is a request for NewPipe itself and that requests for adding a new service need to be made at [NewPipeExtractor](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipeExtractor/issues).\n- [X] I have taken the time to fill in all the required details. I understand that the feature request will be dismissed otherwise.\n- [X] This issue contains only one feature request.\n- [X] I have read and understood the [contribution guidelines](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/blob/dev/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md).\n\n### Feature description\n\nJust as videos you've watched show the watchtime in a red bar on the bottom, I want videos you see in the wild (e.g. suggested under a video you're watching, or in trending) to show something to mark them as in a playlist _you've made_ (to my mind marking videos from playlists you've saved would be less helpful unless marked differently).\r\n\r\nSimilar idea for channels you've subscribed to too.\n\n### Why do you want this feature?\n\nFor Playlists:\r\nNot accidentally putting a video in a \"watch later\" style playlist twice or in two different playlists.\r\n\r\nReminding yourself to get back to a video you put in a \"to get back to\" style playlist in case you accidentally don't see it.\r\n\r\nFor Channel Subscribtions:\r\nNot accidentally watching a video from a different channel with a similar name or style of titling + thumbnailing.\r\n\r\nGenerally (in my opinion) showing more information with little to no extra eye clutter is always a good thing.\n\n### Additional information\n\nI made a sketch on a screenshot of some examples that might work:\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"IMG_20230328_192055\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68761174/228413145-b49b5258-1d55-4131-8052-cd697901af79.jpg\" width=270 />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAdditionally, in case anything I added is too small to see, I made one with large red circles around them to mark them out (messy, I know):\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"IMG_20230328_192241\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68761174/228413330-fc62eb28-59ba-43b2-beb9-910f91374ea9.jpg\" width=270 />\r\n\r\n\r\nIdeas in these examples (playlists):\r\n\r\n- Underlining video's name on videos in a playlist\r\n- Putting a mark next to video's name of videos in a playlist (either side)\r\n- Writing Saved or Playlisted next to video age\r\n- Putting a marking next to video age or channel name\r\n- Putting a marking on the top corner of a video thumbnail\r\n- Putting a box around the whole video (thinner then shown)\r\n- Putting a box around video the thumbnail\r\n\r\n\r\nIdeas in these examples (subscribed channels)\r\n\r\n- Putting the channel name in white\r\n- Underlining the channel name\r\n- Putting a marking next to the channel name (either side)",
